import { Card, Container,Row,Col } from 'react-bootstrap' import './category.css' import gallery from '../../gallery' import emojibook from '../../emojibook' import TopBar from '../../components/topbar/TopBar' import { useParams } from 'react-router' export default function Category() { let {id}=useParams(); return ( <>
{ emojibook.filter(emoji=>emoji.gallery_id==id).map((emoji,index)=>( {emoji.name} {emoji.meaning} ))}
) }
